            <h2>Executive Summary</h2>
            <p>This competitive intelligence analysis examines the rapid emergence and adoption of Pulsed Field Ablation (PFA) technology in the cardiac electrophysiology market. Using automated data extraction and visualization techniques, we present evidence of market disruption, key player positioning, and strategic opportunities.</p>
            
