                    <strong>Patent Filing Acceleration:</strong> Multiple PFA system patents published in 2024-2025, including advanced pulse period modulation (WO2025128468A1) indicating continued innovation velocity.[3]
                </div>
                <div class="key-finding">
                    <strong>Clinical Trials Expansion:</strong> New prospective RCTs (PRAISE trial, NCT06791629) directly comparing PFA vs RF for persistent AF, positioning PFA as definitive treatment modality.[4]
